snippet.title: WalkScape Closed Beta TEASER
snippet.description:
Coming to iOS and Android! 

WalkScape is a game inspired by good ol' RuneScape. But this game has one major trick up its sleeve: you don't play actively, but instead gain progress by walking.

Link to our website, and other improtant links are available in our account's about page:
https://www.youtube.com/@WalkScaper/about
